### ============================================================
### ai-screen API 测试文件
### 使用 VS Code REST Client 或 IntelliJ HTTP Client 运行
### ============================================================

### 环境变量
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@aiToken = your-ai-token-here-change-in-production
@screenId = screen_mogi28di_dkfyj6sls

### ============================================================
### 基础
### ============================================================

### GET 首页 (SPA入口)
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### ============================================================
### AI Agent API — 查询屏幕
### ============================================================

### 查询所有屏幕
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/screens
Authorization: Bearer {{aiToken}}

### ============================================================
### AI Agent API — 注册/确认屏幕
### ============================================================

### 确认注册 pending 屏幕
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/screens/{{screenId}}/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{aiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name_en": "Living Room TV",
  "name_zh": "客厅电视",
  "width": 1920,
  "height": 1080
}

### ============================================================
### AI Agent API — 编辑屏幕
### ============================================================

### 编辑屏幕名称
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/screens/{{screenId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{aiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name_en": "Living Room TV Updated",
  "name_zh": "客厅电视(已更新)",
  "width": 3840,
  "height": 2160
}

### 只编辑部分字段（不传尺寸）
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/screens/{{screenId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{aiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name_en": "Living Room TV V2"
}

### ============================================================
### AI Agent API — 投影
### ============================================================

### 投影 inline_html
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/screens/{{screenId}}/project
Authorization: Bearer {{aiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "inline_html",
  "content": "<div style=\"text-align:center;padding:40px;color:white;background:#222;height:100vh;\"><h1>Hello from AI Agent</h1><p>Current time: <span id=\"t\"></span></p></div><script>setInterval(()=>document.getElementById('t').textContent=new Date().toLocaleTimeString(),1000)</script>"
}

### 投影 iframe
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/screens/{{screenId}}/project
Authorization: Bearer {{aiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "iframe",
  "content": "https://example.com"
}

### 投影 inline_html + 附件
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/screens/{{screenId}}/project
Authorization: Bearer {{aiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "inline_html",
  "content": "<div style=\"padding:40px;\"><h1>Image Preview</h1><img src=\"ATTACHMENT_PLACEHOLDER\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"/></div>",
  "attachment_url": "/attachments/your-attachment-id?t=your-attachment-token"
}

### ============================================================
### AI Agent API — 附件
### ============================================================

### 上传附件 (multipart)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attachments
Authorization: Bearer {{aiToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< demo.html
------FormBoundary--

### 访问附件 (屏幕端，需要附件 token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/attachments/your-attachment-id?t=your-attachment-token

### ============================================================
### AI Agent API — 失效/删除
### ============================================================

### 失效屏幕（断开 WebSocket）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/screens/{{screenId}}/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{aiToken}}

### 删除屏幕
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/screens/{{screenId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{aiToken}}

### ============================================================
### 错误场景
### ============================================================

### 缺少 Authorization
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/screens

### 错误的 Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/screens
Authorization: Bearer wrong-token

### 确认不存在的屏幕（返回 404）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/screens/non-existent-screen/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{aiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name_en": "Test",
  "name_zh": "测试"
}

### 缺少必填字段 name_en
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/screens/{{screenId}}/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{aiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name_zh": "只有中文名"
}

### 无效投影类型
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/screens/{{screenId}}/project
Authorization: Bearer {{aiToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "invalid_type",
  "content": "test"
}

### ============================================================
### WebSocket 连接 (不能用 REST Client 测试，用 wscat 代替)
### ============================================================
### 新屏幕注册: wscat -c "ws://localhost:3000/ws?token=pending&screen_id=screen_xxx&w=1920&h=1080"
### 已注册屏幕: wscat -c "ws://localhost:3000/ws?token=<screen_token>&w=1920&h=1080"
